@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

autonumber
autoactivate on

Actor "Client" as client
participant "UI" as ui
participant "restDB" as restdb

note over client, restdb: The user goes to the Settings screen, clicks on the "LANGUAGE" button and selects a language

client -> ui: Selects a language
    ui -> restdb: Finds the user in the database
    restdb --> ui: User's id
    ui -> restdb: Sends new language preference
        restdb -> restdb: Updates user information
        restdb --> restdb
    restdb --> ui
ui --> client

@enduml